## Phase 14: Rust Redisplay Engine üî• NEW

### Overview

**Decision:** Rewrite Emacs redisplay engine (`xdisp.c`) in pure Rust.

**Rationale:**
- Current hybrid approach (Emacs incremental redisplay + Rust rendering) has fundamental architectural mismatch
- Emacs assumes backend retains pixels; our GPU approach rebuilds each frame
- Rust ecosystem provides excellent libraries for text layout (cosmic-text, tree-sitter)
- Clean architecture enables GPU-native rendering with animations

